premise_source_doc_sentence: SPECTRE  (  SPecial Executive for Counter-intelligence , Terrorism , Revenge and Extortion  )  is a fictional organisation featured in the James Bond novels by Ian Fleming , the films based on those novels , and James Bond video games .
